# Rules sync (same change set)

Cursor rules are living docs. If you change code in the left column, **read** the matching rule(s) before editing and **update** them before you finish — same task, same response.

## Core & app (architecture)

| If you edit | Update these rules |
|-------------|-------------------|
| `src/app/**`, `src/middleware.ts` | `project-architecture.mdc` |
| `src/core/**` (blocks, data, routing, types, i18n, seo, theme) | `project-architecture.mdc` |
| `src/shared/**` (except tenant-only UI) | `project-architecture.mdc` |
| `.github/workflows/**`, monorepo layout | `project-architecture.mdc` |
| `package.json` scripts, `scripts/prepare-tenant.js` | `project-architecture.mdc`, `new-tenant-checklist.mdc` |

## Blocks & templates

| If you edit | Update these rules |
|-------------|-------------------|
| `src/core/blocks/**`, `src/shared/components/blocks/**` | `block-system.mdc`, `project-architecture.mdc` |
| `src/tenants/*/blocks/**`, `src/tenants/*/templates/**` | `block-system.mdc` + that tenant's `catalog.mdc` |
| `src/app/[domain]/layout.tsx` (theme/analytics only) | `block-system.mdc`, `project-architecture.mdc` |

## Data & mock content

| If you edit | Update these rules |
|-------------|-------------------|
| `src/core/mock-data.ts/**` | `mock-data-pages.mdc` + tenant `catalog.mdc` (see below) |
| `src/core/data/adapters/**` | `project-architecture.mdc`, `mock-data-pages.mdc` |

## Tenant-specific

| If you edit | Update these rules |
|-------------|-------------------|
| `src/tenants/vukans-bike/**` or `mock-data.ts/vukans-bike/**` | `tenants/vukans-bike/catalog.mdc` |
| `src/tenants/resort-example/**` or `mock-data.ts/resort/**` | `tenants/resort-example/catalog.mdc` |
| `src/tenants/*/integrations/**` | `tenant-integrations.mdc` + tenant `catalog.mdc` |
| `src/tenants/*/services/**` | tenant `catalog.mdc`, `block-system.mdc` (data contracts) |
